{"word":"G2554 - κακοποιέω - kakopoiéō - kak-op-oy-eh'-o - Do evil","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κακοποιέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kakopoiéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kak-op-oy-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Do evil</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தீமைசெய்"},{"paragraph":"1. to do harm"},{"paragraph":"2. to do evil, do wrong"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2555 - κακοποιός - kakopoiós - kak-op-oy-os'/2555\">G2555</a>; to <i>be a bad doer</i>, that is, (objectively) to <i>injure</i>, or (generally) to <i>sin:</i> - do (-ing) evil.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1573/1573\">G1573</a>, <a href=\"#/G172/172\">G172</a>, <a href=\"#/G2549/2549\">G2549</a>, <a href=\"#/G2550/2550\">G2550</a>, <a href=\"#/G2554/2554\">G2554</a>, <a href=\"#/G2555/2555\">G2555</a>, <a href=\"#/G2556/2556\">G2556</a>, <a href=\"#/G2557/2557\">G2557</a>, <a href=\"#/G420/420\">G420</a>"}]}